quran[13]{c,v,t}:
  20,52,kaha ke un ka ilm mere perwar-digaar ko hai ( jo ) kitaab mein ( likha howa hai ). mera perwar-digaar nah chokta hai nah bhulta hai
  20,53,woh ( wohi to hai ) jis ne tum logon ke liye zameen ko farsh banaya aur is mein tumahray liye raste jari kiye aur aasman se pani barsaya. phir is se anwaa o iqsaam ki mukhtalif roideedgiyan peda kee
  20,54,ke ( khud bhi ) khao aur apne charpayon ko bhi churao. be shak un ( baton ) mein aqal walon ke liye ( bohat si ) nishanain hain
  20,55,isi ( zameen ) se hum tum ko pedakiya aur isi mein tumhe lota-ayn ge aur isi se doosri dafaa nikalen ge
  20,56,aur hum ne firaon ko apni sab nishanain deikhein magar woh takzib o ankaar hi karta raha
  20,57,kehnay laga ke moose tum hamaray paas is liye aeye ho ke apne jaadoo ( ke zor ) se hamein hamaray malik se nikaal do
  20,58,to hum bhi tumahray maqabil aisa hi jaadoo layein ge to hamaray aur apne darmain aik waqt muqarrar kar lau ke nah to hum is ke khilaaf karen aur nah tum ( aur yeh muqaabla ) aik hamwar maidan mein ( hoga )
  20,59,moose ne kaha aap ke liye ( muqablay ka ) din no roz ( muqarrarkiya jata hai ) aur yeh ke log is din chaasht ke waqt ikhatay ho jaien
  20,60,to firaon lout gaya aur apne samaan jama karkay phir aaya
  20,61,moose ne un ( gado garon) se kaha ke haae tumhari kambakhti. khuda par jhoot iftira nah karo ke woh tumhe azaab se fanaa kardey ga aur jis ne iftirakiya woh namuraad raha
  20,62,to woh baahum apne muamlay mein jhgrhane aur chupkay chupkay sargoshi karne lagey
  20,63,kehnay lagey yeh dono jadugar hain chahtay hain ke apne jaadoo ( ke zor ) se tum ko tumahray malik se nikal den aur tumahray shaista mazhab ko nabood kar dein
  20,64,to tum ( jaadoo ka ) samaan akatha karlo aur phir qitaar bandh kar aao. aaj jo ghalib raha wohi kamyaab howa
